f answered scores for questions 6–10 (0–15)"}, "answered_count": {"type": "integer", "description": "Number of items with answered=true (0–10)"}, "interpretation": {"enum": ["No significant distress", "Mild emotional stress", "Emotional concern present", "Moderate distress", "High distress"], "type": "string", "description": "Distress tier based on total_score"}, "clinical_summary": {"type": "string", "description": "1–2 sentence psychologist-style impression integrating evidence across items"}, "recommended_action": {"enum": ["Routine observation", "Provide reassurance / Brief counselling", "Monitor / consider psychologist referral", "Refer to psychologist", "Immediate referral to psychologist"], "type": "string", "description": "Clinical action matching the interpretation tier"}, "score_reliability_note": {"type": "string", "description": "Non-empty caveat only when fewer than 70% of items were answered (<7 of 10); empty string otherwise"}}, "description": "Inpatient psychology assessment (10 items, 0–30) inferred from conversation + voice"}}}', '2026-04-24 08:42:55.835529+00', 'segment_definition:PSYCHOLOGY_IP_ASSESS:update', 'fc6673d76ae5411cd01450c5ad56bb90fbcf23c62732d80249f9c632e990e57a', 'f90e4d865296afcafabcc47f31dbf8e75003c3f703b9a8046d37e22431fc0306', '{}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
