s admissions with dates and details"}}, "description": "Previous cardiac history and relevant cardiac workup"}, "followUp": {"type": "object", "properties": {"review_date": {"type": "string", "description": "Next review date in DD-MM-YYYY format. Always an explicit calendar date — resolve any relative phrase the doctor uses (e.g., ''in 10 days'', ''after 2 weeks'', ''next month'') into a DD-MM-YYYY date using TODAY''S DATE from the extraction context as the anchor. Return \"\" (empty string) only if no follow-up timing was mentioned at all"}, "other_instructions": {"type": "string", "description": "Contingency/warning signs, diet, activity, monitoring, and lifestyle advice"}, "special_instructions": {"type": "string", "description": "Immediate actions, what to bring, and patient-specific instructions"}}}, "allergies": {"type": "string", "description": "Known allergies or ''NO KNOWN ALLERGY'' if none"}, "diagnosis": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "properties": {"code": {"type": "string", "description": "ICD-10 code (e.g., ''I50.9'')"}, "name": {"type": "string", "description": "Diagnosis name with comments"}, "type": {"type": "string", "description": "Primary or Secondary"}}}, "description": "List of diagnoses with type and ICD-10 codes"}, "labResults": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "properties": {"result": {"type": "string", "description": "Result with units"}, "ref_range": {"type": "string", "description": "Reference range"}, "test_name": {"type": "string", "description": "Test name with date"}, "parameter_name": {"type": "string", "description": "Parameter name"}}}, "description": "Lab results table"}, "examination": {"type": "object", "properties": {"systemic": {"type": "object", "properties": {"cns": {"type": "string", "description": "CNS findings"}, "cvs": {"type": "string", "description": "CVS findings"}, "respiratory": {"type": "string", "description": "RS findings"}}, "description": "Systemic examination findings"}, "cardiac_ex