**Description:** Extract the consultant''s narrative summary of the case â€” a free-text synthesis that ties together findings from the examinations and the Nidhana Panchaka framework into a working clinical impression. This is the consultant''s prose explanation, distinct from the structured diagnostic conclusions in SAMPRAPTI and the named diagnosis in DIAGNOSIS.

