### 17. REFERRAL DETAILS

### 15. REFERRAL DETAILS (Only if referral mentioned)                                                                                                                            
                  
  **Extraction Rules:**
  - ✅ Include if the patient was referred BY another doctor, OR if the current doctor is referring the patient TO a specialist, or both
  - ✅ **referred_by**: The doctor/facility who referred the patient to the current consultation. Look for phrases like "referred by Dr. X", "sent by Dr. X", "patient came from
  Dr. X''s clinic"                                                                                                                                                                  
  - ✅ **referred_to**: The doctor/specialist the current doctor is referring the patient TO. Include name + specialty when mentioned (e.g., ''Dr. Gowri - Diabetic specialist'')
  - ✅ **reason_for_referral**: Why the referral is being made (for referred-to only)                                                                                              
  - ✅ **referral_urgency**: Routine / Urgent / Emergency (for referred-to only)                                                                                                   
  - ✅ **referral_location**: Hospital/department/clinic for the referral (for referred-to only)                                                                                   
  - ❌ Omit this entire segment if no referral in either direction is mentioned                                                                                                    
  - ❌ Do NOT confuse referred_by (who sent the patient here) with referred_to (where the patient is being sent next)                                                              
   
  **Example — patient referred by one doctor, being referred to another:**                                                                                                         
  {               
    "referred_by": "Dr. Kumar - General Physician, City Clinic",                                                                                                                   
    "referred_to": "Dr. Sharma - Cardiologist",
    "reason_for_referral": "Uncontrolled hypertension requiring specialist evaluation",
    "referral_urgency": "Routine",                                                                                                                                                 
    "referral_location": "Apollo Cardiology Department"
  }                                                                                                                                                                                
                  
  **Example — only referred by (no onward referral):**
  {
    "referred_by": "Dr. Priya - Pediatrician",
    "referred_to": "",                                                                                                                                                             
    "reason_for_referral": "",
    "referral_urgency": "",                                                                                                                                                        
    "referral_location": ""
