- caffeine_intake: "None" / "1 serving/day" / "2â€“3 servings/day" / ">3 servings/day"

**Food Frequency:**
- fresh_fruit_servings_per_day: "0" / "1â€“2" / "3â€“5" / "6+"
- whole_vegetables_servings_per_day: "0" / "1â€“2" / "3â€“5" / "6+"
- whole_grains_legumes_starches_per_day: "0" / "1â€“2" / "3â€“5" / "6+"
