- added_sugar_elimination_seriousness: "You bet" / "Fairly" / "Not very" / "No"
- white_flour_consumption: "Zero" / "Light" / "Medium" / "Heavy"
- sweets_salty_snacks_consumption: "Minimal" / "Light" / "Medium" / "Heavy"
- meat_poultry_fish_meals_per_week: "0â€“1" / "2â€“5" / "6â€“11" / "12+"
- vegetable_oil_meals_per_week: "0â€“1" / "2â€“5" / "6â€“11" / "12+"

**Eating Patterns (Quantitative):**
