- unsustainable_or_harmful_experience: free text â€” anything that felt unsustainable or harmful from past diets, or ""
- bad_reactions_to_food: free text â€” sensitivities or allergies list, or ""
- foods_currently_avoided: free text â€” particular foods avoided, or ""
