- ✅ For SIB plans, the highest dose level goes in `rt_dose_gy`; the elective dose levels go in `additional_phases`.
- ✅ For combined EBRT + brachy, EBRT in main fields, brachy in `additional_phases`.
- ❌ Do NOT invent dose / fractions / technique to fit a template. If doctor only stated dose, leave fractions "" rather than guessing.
- ❌ Do NOT include impression / staging / risk — those belong in IMPRESSION_AND_PLAN.
- ❌ Do NOT duplicate ADT / hormonal therapy details that belong in EXAMINATION unless they are a key plan modifier (concurrent or sequential to RT).

