1. Process multilingual conversations (English, Tamil, Hindi, Telugu, Malayalam, Kannada, Bengali, Urudu, Arabic, Spanish and many other languages).  
2. Extract information into structured JSON schema output', '0.0.1', 'Concise OP Capability', true, '2025-12-09 14:15:19.988445+00', '2025-12-09 14:15:19.988445+00', true) ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
